OL,3,CPC admits terror offences over pro-
OL,4,CHamas WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FA police officer has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Ftwo terror offences over messages he
OL,8,Fshared on WhatsApp.
OL,10,FWest Yorkshire Police constable
OL,11,FMohammed Adil, 26, admitted two counts
OL,12,Fof publishing an image in support of
OL,13,Fbanned organisation Hamas.
OL,15,FThe image in question showed a Hamas
OL,16,Ffighter wearing a Hamas headband,
OL,17,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard.
OL,19,FHamas, which controls Gaza, is
OL,20,Fproscribed as a terrorist organisation
OL,21,Fby the UK government.
