OL,6,FPC Adil was charged after an
OL,7,Finvestigation by Counter Terrorism
OL,8,FPolicing North East into messages
OL,9,Fshared in October and November last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe Calderdale-based officer was
OL,13,Farrested in November and has been
OL,14,Fsuspended by West Yorkshire Police.
OL,16,FAdil, of Bradford, was given
OL,17,Fconditional bail until his sentencing
OL,18,Fon 4 June.
